755866886;"I'm A Little Teapot for iPad";"Help Mrs Teapot set the table for a tea party!

Created by Listening and Spoken Language Specialists in conjunction with Early Childhood Teachers, I’m a Little Teapot is a highly interactive learning experience. The app is full of wonderful educational ideas and animated interactive games to encourage the development of listening and language skills in young children. Families of children who have reduced hearing or language problems will find the app particularly useful.
I’m a Little Teapot has been designed as a cooperative app for parents and children so they can participate in a variety of shared activities together.
The app is divided into three sections:
1. Ideas

This section provides strategies and techniques, including instructional videos on how to use I’m a Little Teapot to develop listening and language skills. This is achieved through interactive play, craft, and ideas on how to sing the song differently. These ideas are grouped together depending on your child’s language level:
-Emerging language
-Putting words together
-Putting sentences together
2. Interactive games

There is a fully animated game with three levels. Each level targets different levels of listening and language skills. With help from mum or dad, your child can choose to play a level that either consolidates or extends their current listening and language abilities. The game is:
-Set the table

Help Mrs Teapot set the table for three tea party guests. Choose different coloured and patterned cups and saucers to set the table and pour the tea. The game introduces different colours (blue, red, yellow, green, pink, orange, brown, black, grey, purple) and shapes (circles, triangles, stars, hearts, stripes).
Each of the levels builds upon your child’s auditory memory.
- Level 1: 1 word descriptor, e.g. choose the blue saucer
- Level 2: 2 word descriptors, e.g. choose the blue saucer with stars
- Level 3: 3 word descriptors, e.g. choose the blue saucer with red stars
PLEASE NOTE: Games are not compatible with iPad VoiceOver screen reader.
3. Music and karaoke
Learn the lyrics to I’m a Little Teapot, alternative versions, and related songs. A karaoke style sing-a-long with music and lyrics is a great way to involve your child in singing.
More apps:
Five Little Monkeys is part of our series on Songs for Listening and Language.
Also available for iPad:
-Old MacDonald
-Row, Row, Row Your Boat
-I’m a Dingle Dangle Scarecrow
-Incy Wincy Spider
-Five Little Monkeys
Also available for iPhone:
-Old MacDonald
FACEBOOK: Join us on Facebook to keep up to date with upcoming apps!
www.facebook.com/nextsense
CONTACT US: For feedback and support email – apps@ridbc.org.au"
582308236;"Anglictina PREMIUM";"#1 aplikace pro anglictinu - vstrebávejte anglictinu zábavne - ucte se bez biflování a prirozene!
Anglictina metodou iSmartLanguage je vedecky podložená a již overená mnoha jejími uživateli jako nejefektivnejší metoda pro výuku cizích jazyku pro samouky!
* Chcete znát význam slovícka? -> Použijte nejaký slovník.
* Chcete preložit celou vetu? -> Použijte nejaký prekladac.
* Chcete cizí jazyk analyzovat? -> Biflujte gramatiku, treba v jazykovce.
* Chcete si zapamatovat jednotlivá slovícka? -> Používejte nejaký kartickový systém (flashcards).
* Chcete cizí jazyk skutecne ovládat a rovnou v nem i myslet, tj. rozumet rodilým mluvcím a mluvit se správným prízvukem bez prekládání? Pak ctete dál.
Naucíte se správnou výslovnost - posloucháte jen opravdové rodilé mluvcí.
Jednotlivé lekce jsou peclive vybrány rodilými mluvcími z USA a UK. Konverzace je tedy založena na praktických situacích, v kterých se mužete bežne ocitnout i vy.
Výhody metody iSmartLanguage:
* ucíte se tím nejprirozenejším zpusobem
* nepotrebujete žádný slovník (máte k dispozici doslovné preklady)
* porozumíte rodilým mluvcím (britští i americtí mluvcí)
* studovat mužete i pasivne - kdekoliv na to dostanete chut
* vynikající pomer cena/výkon
Aplikace obsahuje:
* Bežnou konverzaci (Klasická anglictina) a Obchodní anglictinu
* 9 hodin nahrávek
* celkove 27 lekcí, 4.085 vet, 58.543 slov
Navíc bonusy:
* Jak studovat anglictinu: 8 minut, 44 vet, 264 unikátních slov
* Hláskování a výslovnost: 7 minut, 18 vet, 158 unikátních slov
* Nepravidelná slovesa: 42 minut, 1.377 vet, 1.873 unikátních slov
Aplikace má snadné a intuitivní ovládání, žádné zbytecnosti nehledejte.
Simuluje anglické prostredí, což je pro výuku anglictiny to nejlepší!
Doporucený postup výuky:
* nejdríve jen poslouchejte (""nasávejte"" význam vet)
* až melodii anglictiny naposloucháte, zacnete si pri poslechu anglictinu také ríkat (v duchu opakovat)

533052266;"Row, Row, Row Your Boat";"Ahoy thar matey, join Pirate Black Mo on the high seas and develop your child’s listening and language skills!

Created by Listening and Spoken Language Specialists in conjunction with Early Childhood Teachers, Row, Row, Row Your Boat is a highly interactive learning experience. The app is full of wonderful educational ideas, animated interactive games, and engaging sounds to encourage the development of listening and language skills in young children. Families of children who have reduced hearing or language difficulties will find the app particularly useful.

Row, Row, Row Your Boat has been designed as a cooperative app for parents and children so they can participate in a variety of shared activities together. These activities are divided into three sections:
1. Ideas

This section provides strategies and techniques, including instructional videos on how to use Row, Row, Row Your Boat to develop listening and language skills. This is achieved through interactive play, craft, and ideas on how to sing the song differently. These ideas are grouped together depending on your child’s language level:
• Emerging language
• Putting words together
• Putting sentences together
2. Interactive games

There are two fully animated games that target different levels of listening and language skills. With help from mum or dad, your child can choose to play a game that either consolidates or extends their current listening and language abilities. The games are:
• Where do they go?

Help Pirate Black Mo sort out where all the vehicles belong – in the air, on land, or in the water, then watch them spring to life and hear the sounds they make. Ten vehicles are included: row boat, sail boat, submarine, car, bike, bus, truck, plane, air balloon, and rocket.
• Collect the treasure!
Help Pirate Black Mo fill his coffers by collecting objects that rhyme. This game introduces early childhood rhyming concepts in a fun, goal orientated way.
PLEASE NOTE: Games are not compatible with VoiceOver screen reader.
3. Music and karaoke
Learn the lyrics to Row, Row, Row Your Boat, alternative versions, and related songs. A karaoke style sing-a-long with music and lyrics is a great way to involve your child in singing.
More apps
Row, Row, Row Your Boat is part of our series on 'Songs for Listening and Language.'

1485216027;"ChristKlang";"Alle Jahre wieder, wenn es draußen kalt und frostig wird entspringt in uns die Sehnsucht mit unseren Liebsten in den wohlig warmen und nach Adventkranz und Weihnachtsbäckerei duftenden Stuben, zusammen zu sitzen. Die köstlichen Kekse von Oma und Mama genießen, die ein oder andere Geschichte erzählen oder anhören und….? Da war doch noch was!
Ach ja es wäre schön….wieder einmal gemeinsam zu singen!

Singen ist nicht nur Balsam für die Seele und Lebensmittel für Geist und Körper. Vielmehr war und ist es Klebstoff zwischen den Generationen, die im gemeinsamen Gesang sofort den Gleichklang ihrer Herzen spüren.

Um die so wichtige Komponente der Adventzeit allen Menschen zu ermöglichen, wurde diese App entwickelt, in der die beliebtesten Advent- und Weihnachtslieder für zwei Stimmen und Gitarrenbegleitung zu finden sind.
Sie können Stimme für Stimme ganz einfach gelernt werden. Und das geht so:

Beim Abspielen der Lieder läuft am Smartphone oder Tablet das Notenbild mit dem Text mit, um so das Erlernen des Liedes zu erleichtern. Zunächst sollte man in der App nur jene der beiden Gesangsstimmen laut lassen, die man lernen möchte. Mit dem Lautstärken-Regler kann man die andere Stimme ganz einfach leiser oder wegschalten.
Hat man die Stimme gelernt, stellt man den Laustärkenregler der gelernten Stimme nun leise und jenen der Stimme, die vom App kommen soll lauter.

Wenn man jetzt seine gelernte Stimme dazu singt, sollte man das Lied schon in vollem akustischen Glanz erklingen hören. Um die eigene Stimme zu überprüfen kann man nun, anstatt auf den Play-Button zu drücken, den Aufnahmemodus durch das Drücken des Mikrophon-Symbols auslösen. Stoppt man die Aufnahme, wechselt das Lied in der Anzeige auf einen Mix-Modus und es erscheinen fünf Bedienfelder.

Die obersten zwei sind die Lautstärkenregler der Originalstimmen 1+2, das dritte Bedienfeld zur Lautstärkeregelung der Gitarre, das vierte zur Regelung der eigenen aufgenommenen Stimme und das fünfte zur Positionierung der Aufnahmespur im Falle von Verzögerungen bei der Aufnahme, die bei unterschiedlichsten Geräten auch unterschiedlich groß sein können. Mit dem Regler kann man dann die eigene Aufnahme so verschieben, dass sie wieder passt und gleichzeitig mit den anderen Audiospuren abgespielt wird.
Wenn man mit der Aufnahme zufrieden ist, drückt man  den Knopf „Mischen und Speichern“ und schon liegt die fertige Aufnahme im  Ordner „Aufgenommenes“.

Im Advent ist es Familien damit möglich, mit Kindern ein paar Weihnachtslieder für das Christkind ganz einfach zu üben, mit Oma, Opa, Tanten und Onkeln neue Lieder zu lernen und alle zusammen mit entzückenden Weihnachtsgeschichten, die unter „Erzähltes“ zu finden sind, zu belohnen.
Die eigenen Aufnahmen können über die App  an Freunde und Verwandte über viele unterschiedliche Dienste, wie Messenger, WhatsApp, Mails, … verschickt werden.

Für den Heiligen Abend gibt es die Möglichkeit, mittels des Button „Geplantes“ ganz einfach ein Programm für die Bescherung anzulegen, indem man sich Lieder aus dem Ordner „Aufgenommenes“ oder Lieder, die als Karaoke Version im Ordner „Gesungenes“ liegen, Geschichten (wie das Weihnachtsevangelium) und Instrumentalstücke aus dem Ordner „Gepieltes“ in das „Programm“ zieht. Bei allen Liedern besteht auch hier noch die Möglichkeit die unterschiedlichen Gesangsstimmen leiser oder sogar ganz weg zu schalten, um das Weihnachtslied nur mit Gitarrenbegleitung vor dem Christbaum dann vielleicht gänzlich selber zu singen.
Das ganze „Programm“ wiederum kann über alle Dienste verschickt werden, sodass man mit den Eltern und Großeltern am Heiligen Abend vor dem Christbaum sängerisch zusammen sein kann.
Wir würden uns freuen Ihnen die Lieder nicht nur ans Herz, sondern auch wieder in den Mund zu legen – denn „Weihnachtslieder soll man selber singen“
Die kostenlose Version beinhaltet 2 Lieder unter ""Gesungenes"". Um alle Lieder, Geschichten und Musik freizuschalten, ist ein In-App-Kauf erforderlich."

1005227156;"future.dj pro - mix everything";"future.dj pro - A new level of mixing perfection
* Mix everything (audio, video, karaoke)

Mashup tracks, mix videos and make song transitions with the greatest of ease with this classic DJ setup (2 or 4-decks and mixer). Thanks to it's intuitive design and powerful features, you will be able to achieve any level of mixing complexity. You can also sit back and Automix an entire party, simply by activating the powerful Automix function.
* real-time stems separation of any song or video into: Vocals, Instruments, Drums
* 8 different user interfaces/skins included (with 2 or 4 decks)
* Perfectly in-sync tracks/beats

You will find the automatic BPM detection very precise allowing you to instantly sync and change between the 2 decks and/or samplers. The smart-sync function guarantees that when you press the Sync button the deck will be in perfect sync with the other one.
* Visualize beats

The waveform graphic displays gives you real time audio signal monitoring, information about the audio signal and the beat rhythm. Each deck has 3 waveforms: a full song waveform and two zoomed-in waveforms. The vertical waveforms allow you to visually align the beats with ease.
* Find your tracks with ease (includes iTunes library integration)

There is a browser, a current-list and a side-list available for finding, organising, previewing and playing your tracks. You can instantly search for tracks and/or filter them by format (be it audio, video or karaoke). Color markers make it even easier to spot your favorite songs, because you can assign different colors to any tracks.
* Create and recall loops, set up cue-points

You can set up seamless loops instantly, by setting In and Out points. You can move the loop or make it shorter or longer on-the-fly. You can also send a loop to one of the 8 sampler slots. You can set/recall instant cue-points (which act like bookmarks into the song) and view them on the waveform.
* Scratch. Reverse. Brake. (works with videos too)

You are free to make real turntable effects by using the waveform displays, as well as the virtual jog-wheels, using MIDI controllers or even real turntables (using the improved timecoded-vinyl engine). You can achieve effects like disk spin effect, scratch, reverse, play, brake, mute, fine-tune cue-points and even 'reverse spin and play' effect.
* Powerful mixer (includes effects)
You can adjust the gain (amplification), equalizer (3 bands), apply and combine different effects (10 effects included), change the musical key, etc.
* Separate headphones output and song pre-listening
You can configure advanced audio routing using up to 8 inputs and outputs. You can use a microphone or turntables and CD players.
* Fullscreen video output to external monitors, projectors, TV
There are several video effects and transitions that you can apply per deck.
* Real-time beat-aware visualizations (shaders)
* Powerful karaoke features including singers rotation list, key pre-adjusting, filler/background music player and more
* Connect multiple MIDI controllers at the same time

There are over 120 zero-configure controllers supported from Pioneer, Numark, Denon, Akai, Akiyama, American Audio, Beamz, Behringer, Beyond Music, Faderfox, Gemini, Hercules, M-Audio, Novation, PCDJ, Reloop, Stanton, Vestax, Zomo, etc.
* Powerful samplers
8 sample players that you can use to play loops or jingles. You can pre-listen, choose to loop or sync them, apply filters, change the tempo/speed, etc.
* Beat-match and Key-match your mixes

For musically perfect mixes you can lock (master tempo) or change the key to your desired one to achieve not only beat-matched but also key-matched performances. The app even detects the key of a song/video to considerably simplify harmonic mixing.
* Record or broadcast your mixes
/// If you have any feedback or just want to say “Hi,” email us info@xylio.com

Our over-attachment to our phones can lead to feelings of loneliness and isolation (*sigh*) making it difficult to connect with people IRL. Join Me Tonight (JMT) strives to change all this by making going out easy and fun, all while minimizing the time you spend on the app. JMT provides a safe environment for people with various interests to connect and do the stuff they love without having to spend hours on the app trying to sort out plan details.

Whether you want to find someone to check out that new lounge downtown with, you’re bored at home, or you just want to meet people while traveling, JMT has you covered. And we’re not just talking about finding dates. It’s a great app for expanding your social circle and organizing group events. Like, the kinds of group events you’re actually into. How many times have you stayed home because you had no one to do sushi and lychee martinis with? Or sit courtside with at a basketball game? Or get your 90’s karaoke on with? Sure, we all have friends, but they’re not always into the same stuff we are. It’s totally cool to kick it solo sometimes, but isn’t everything more fun with a crew, or a date, or a homie? That’s what JMT is for!
AWESOME PERKS:
• No endless back and forth textathons –– events can only be created a maximum of 7 days in advance. Done...and done.
• No wasting time figuring out where to go or what to do –– create / choose events within set categories, chat, and finalize plans in a few swift clicks (peace out, wafflers)
• No awkward moments when the bill comes –– confirm in advance who pays (or if you’ll go Dutch)
• No more, “hey, you up?” texts at 2AM –– we don’t allow events between 12AM and 7AM (yeah, we thought of that)
• “Net-flix and chill” is OUT –– JMT Events are strictly limited to public locations (you’re welcome)
• Finally –– Netflix, we still love you (for the shows)
HOW IT WORKS:
1) Register and create your profile
2) Create an event and spread the word to JMT users in your area, users will tap to let you know they are interested in joining you
OR
Browse events to see what others are up to. If you’re interested in joining, tap the prompt to let them know!
3) Choose which interested users you want to join you
4) Get notified when there’s mutual interest - this initiates the chat feature so you can finalize plans.
5) Go out tonight and have fun!
By downloading or using the Join Me Tonight app, you are agreeing to our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, available at
https://joinmetonight.com/privacy-policy/
https://JoinMeTonight.com/terms/
Have a question or would like to get in touch with us?
Visit https://www.JoinMeTonight.com

1123061704";"AirJamz Music";"AirJamz Music is the official app for AirJamz — The Connected Toy That Rocks. Just connect your AirJamz by Bluetooth to the app on your mobile device – Then pick a song and strum along or use any moves you want to create music!
Visit playairjamz.com or find us on Amazon to get your own.
Highlights:

• 100+ unique instruments & sounds to play — iconic air guitar riffs, air drums, air keys, SFX and more.

We’ve all played air guitar and it’s an awesome feeling. With AirJamz, instead of pretending to play along to that epic guitar solo, you get to create your own. Your moves make music! No experience necessary, just pick up and play.

It looks like a guitar pick, but you can use it to play the drums, keys and tons of other instruments too. Love EDM, Pop or Country? AirJamz has them all. And if you like music games or karaoke, you’ll love AirJamz – it gets the whole house rocking!

Play on your own, or make it a group activity; up to 4 people can connect and play at the same time, so it's great for solo or family play. Whether you're playing air guitar, or just want to dance around to make music, the experience is up to you.
AirJamz is brought to you from the team at Zivix — Quality you can trust from the makers of the jamstik+ SmartGuitar.
Don't have an AirJamz? Visit www.playairjamz.com to learn more and get your own!"

1441160645;"SoMusiX";"...'You have a tune in mind? A catchy rhythm beating with Your heart? Daydreaming of a new vibe, string or chord? Imagined a never-before heard melody, a uniquely new, sweet harmony?

That's all You need. Record even just a few seconds of it by the App, upload it to SoMusix’s Cloud, and the let community turn it into a full piece of Music. Or select someone else’s idea that You like, edit it, or extend it by Your instrumental performance, singing, or any other audible art.

SoMusiX - or Social Music eXperiment - is a high concept, Internet & Mobile Application-based solution allowing simple or complex, short or long, but unique musical ‘ideas’; like just a few tones, rhythms, chords, vocal pieces to be recorded & merged together by the community, to create fascinating new songs & pieces of audible art, without any limitation to genre(s), geographical or cultural, real or presumed borders, limitations, differences or other obstacles.

When a new recording is uploaded, a new musical ‘existence’ is created, inheriting the style, taste & mood of its creator. It immediately starts searching for other artists who might contribute to its evolution, - follows, contacts & invites them, even sends messages; it stars learning, becoming an individual. MusiX are alive.

Follow Your MusiX’s evolution, or chose another! You can watch & listen to any & all current editing stages of any & all the uploaded songs, recordings in live, real-time. You can see how many other people are listening to it, liking it, you can read their comments, suggestions. You can check any & all remixed audio versions, and listen to new tracks, recordings which other artists are adding to it; you can even see how Your Music is „feeling” at the moment.

Follow as many other MusiX as You wish, borrow other artist’s recordings, and create new MusiX of Your own taste by using them. Extend them with Your audible ideas, mix it with tracks borrowed from elsewhere,  don’t be afraid to cross musical genres!

Feeling inspired again? Re-join editing again, at any time or stage, regardless of whether it was Your recording, or someone else’s music. Comment it, suggest or upload new tracks, lyrics or scores. You are free to alter the evolution of any musical piece - like everyone else can  - and You don’t need to worry. You’ll never overwrite or interfere with each other’s editings.

What’s Yours is Yours - Anyone can borrow everyone else’s recordings, in order to create totally new Musical pieces of any taste or style, but the system never forgets who owns the original. Doesn’t matter who modifies it in what way, or what it becomes, any new Musix inherits all original copyrights.

Be a musical influencer! Use Your musical talent, sharing Your audible ideas & passion. You can be musical influencer not only by Your recordings; but also by editing, remixing, remastering, transposing any genres of music. Be a DJ or a orchestral conductor - or both. Shine.

You’re not stranded any more! You can be playing in / be part of as many bands & orchestras as You wish simultaneously. Enjoy sharing your audible art  with anyone You would like to, from any musical culture, from any part of the world, without limitations.
This is no Karaoke. SoMusix is not about replaying already existing pieces of audible art. It is about the common sensation of live, limitless, new musical creation.
No need to be a musician - Here You can become a star without any musical education. All You need is a tune, a musical idea of any kind. Try it, play with it!
Can not sing or play a given  instrument? No problem :) You can also upload lyrics, or even musical score sheets that You composed, and invite other artists to perform it.

SoMusiX is not only intended for singers, performers or musicians. It is for everyone to experiment with millions of mixing variations in a world of continuously evolving audible art, joyful sensation and creative musical inspiration."

column1: 1435981626;"Party Hunt - Nightlife Guide";"Discover and immerse yourself in the vibrant music scene of Goa, Himachal, and Pune with Party Hunt, the ultimate mobile app for music lovers. Whether you're a local resident or a tourist, Party Hunt is your go-to tool for exploring and experiencing the best music events in these regions. Find your perfect music event with our user-friendly interface and powerful features.

Event Discovery: Easily search for music events based on location, date, genre, and more. Our interactive map conveniently displays event locations and distances from your current position, making it easy to plan your night in Goa, Himachal, or Pune.

Detailed Event Listings: Get all the important event details at a glance, including venue information, start and end times, featured performers, and more. Browse through photos and videos of past events to get a taste of the vibrant atmosphere.

Event Promotion: Are you organising a music event? Utilise Party Hunt to reach a large audience. Create an event listing, add all the necessary details, and effortlessly share it with your followers on social media. The more people who know about your event, the greater its potential for success!

Connect with Music Lovers: Stay connected with like-minded music enthusiasts and stay up-to-date on the latest events. Follow your favourite DJs, venues, and event organisers to receive notifications about new events and updates. Engage in conversations, share photos and videos, and join groups to discuss music, nightlife, and more.

Reward System: Party Hunt rewards you for promoting events, sharing experiences, and connecting with others. Earn points by sharing events, posting content, and inviting friends to join the app. Redeem your points for exclusive rewards, such as VIP access and ticket discounts.
LOCATIONS: Discover events in Goa, Himachal, and Pune. Explore the vibrant music scenes in Arambol, Anjuna, Vagator, South Goa, Manali, Kasol, Dharamshala, Shimla, and more.
MUSIC GENRES: Explore a wide range of music genres, including Rock, Bollywood, Trance, Reggae, Jazz, Techno, Blues, Country, Metal, Classical, Electronic, Hip Hop, Latin, and Pop.
PARTY STYLES: Choose from a variety of party styles, such as Festival, After Party, Live Concert, Open Mic, Pool Party, Karaoke, Jamming, Clubbing, Beach Party, Ecstatic Dance, and Rave.

Party Hunt is your ultimate companion for discovering, promoting, and connecting with the music scene in Goa, Himachal, and Pune. Experience the best of their vibrant nightlife, whether you're a local or a tourist. Join the party today and dive into India's vibrant music scene! Download Party Hunt now."

985902912;"Karaoke List Vietnam";".   Karaoke List Pro là ung dung MIEN PHÍ ho tro tìm kiem mã so bài hát karaoke voi nhieu tính nang noi bat. Kho DANH SÁCH bài hát khong lo lên toi gan 40.000 bài hát cung cap danh sách bài hát cho hau het các dau karaoke pho bien hien nay bao gom: Arirang, California, Musiccore, Viet KTV, ... Dã cap nhat vol moi nhat vol 64.
Tính nang noi bat:
»  Tìm kiem dia diem hát karaoke gan vi trí cua ban nhat.
»  Tìm kiem bài hát theo thoi gian thuc cuc nhanh - gõ moi ký tu deu hien thi ngay ket qua mà không bi giat. Dây là tính nang mà nhieu ung dung tìm kiem bài hát khác không có.
»  Tìm nhanh bài hát theo tên, mã so, tác gia, loi dau bài hát.
»  Tìm nhanh bài hát theo bat cu doan nào cua tên bài hát hay loi bài hát.
»  Tìm cuc nhanh bài hát dua vào ký tu dau bài hát. Ví du: 'cdty' => 'Con duong tình yêu'.
»  Voi 5 loai hieu ung menu rat chuyên nghiep.
»  Cùng voi rat nhieu giao dien tuyet dep tu Nam tính den Nu tính dáp ung moi so thích khác nhau.
Tính nang khác:
»  Hien thi tat ca gan 40.000 bài hát trong cùng mot danh sách, thích hop de ban tìm kiem bat cu bài hát nào ngay ca khi không biet loai dau karaoke là loai gì. Rat hap dan.
»  Hien thi tat ca bài hát theo danh sách 5 so, 6 so, Tieng Viet và Tieng Anh.
»  Hien thi danh sách bài hát theo tung loai dau karaoke, giúp viec tìm kiem cua ban nhanh hon.
» Hien thi danh sách bài hát theo album Volume.
» Hien thi danh sách bài hát theo bang chu cái a, b, c ...
» Cho phép ban luu tru danh sách bài hát yêu thích de tien cho viec xem lai.
» Cap nhat thuong xuyên nhanh chóng khi có vol moi.
Luu ý:

-  Dây là ung dung tra cuu mã so bài hát voi kho luu tru lên den gan 40.000 bài hát và duoc chia ra làm nhieu loai danh sách bài hát nhat hien nay tai viet nam. Viec này dong nghia voi viec nó se giúp cho ban có nhieu lua chon, và viec tra cuu se nhanh hon rat nhieu."

1161096079;"Quan lý bán hàng ONLINE ZaPOS";"ZaPOS Pro Giai pháp Quan lý bán hàng thông minh, toàn dien

Giai pháp su dung tablet, smartphone hien có cua nhân viên, quan lý,... de van hành he thong mot cách toi uu và thiet thuc nhat.

ZaPOS khai thác mã QR vào san pham de dua ra nhung tính nang ung dung QR het suc thiet thuc nhu: Order thông minh, dat hàng, tích diem...

ZaPOS ho tro Wifi/3G/4G/5G do vay moi thiet bi gan nhu không gap khó khan khi ket noi he thong.
* Cloud Storage
Du lieu luu tru Cloud do vay khách hàng hoàn toàn yên tâm ve du lieu khi thiet bi bán hàng gap van de nhu: hong hóc, thay doi thiet bi moi...
*** Tính nang chính cua san pham
ZaPOS Cung cap giai pháp bán hàng toàn dien, day du tính nang và ho tro tích hop hau het các thiet bi nhu máy tính, dien thoai, máy tính bang, cân dien tu, ...
01. Quan lý bán hàng
ZaPOS cung cap công cu bán hàng don gian, de su dung và phù hop voi rat nhieu linh vuc kinh doanh khác nhau nhu: nhà hàng, cà phê, bar, karaoke, cua hàng, siêu thi mini, ...
02. Quan lý nhap xuat, kiem kê kho
Quan lý xuat nhap hàng, kiem kê hàng ton là công cu ho tro dac luc cho viec kiem soát hàng bán, hàng ton, that thoát mot cách nhanh nhat hieu qua nhat.
03. Quan lý thông tin khách hàng
Công cu quan lý và cham sóc khách hàng se giúp tang luong khách hàng trung thành, giúp giam chi phí bán hàng nho tiep thi lai, tang doanh so...
04. Công cu quan lý tài chính
ZaPOS Cung cap mot công cu quan lý tài chính het suc don gian và linh dong trong viec xu lý và quan lý dòng tien vào ra rõ ràng minh bach.

ZaPOS ho tro các don vi kinh doanh có nhieu diem bán hàng, nhieu cua hàng truc thuoc... thuc hien viec quan lý van hành bang viec liên ket các co so bán le thành chuoi cua hàng.

Là công cu quan lý quyen truy cap (cap và phân quyen cho nhieu thiet bi, nguoi dùng khác nhau); quan lý nhat ký hoat dong giúp nguoi quan lý kiem soát và truy vet du lieu he thong cuc kì hieu qua.
*** Tai sao lai lua chon giai pháp ZaPOS cua chúng tôi?
- Giai pháp toàn dien
ZaPOS cung cap mot giai pháp quan lý bán hàng mang tính toàn dien trên nhieu nên tang và thiet bi hien nay.

ZaPOS luôn lay chat luong san pham và dich vu sau bán hàng làm su hài lòng và muc tiêu huong toi.

ZaPOS van hành theo mô hình cloud server do vay khách hàng luôn an tâm ve mat du lieu bán hàng.

ZaPOS duoc thiet ke huong toi moi mô hình bán hàng nói chung do vay có the tùy bien theo yêu cau riêng cho moi khách hàng khi su dung.

1320788126";"KiotViet Nhân viên Nhà hàng";"KiotViet – Phan mem quan lý Bar-Café-Nhà hàng-Karaoke, tien loi, de thao tác, tiet kiem chi phí voi hàng ngàn nhà hàng dang su dung.

Giúp ban kiem soát chat che tu khâu tiep dón, sap bàn, den goi món an/do uong, che bien, phuc vu khách hàng và thanh toán. Ban có the su dung KiotViet trên máy tính, máy tính bang hay dien thoai di dong.
Nhung tính nang, loi ích noi bat mà KiotViet mang toi cho ban:
? QUAN LÝ PHÒNG/BÀN:

Giúp ban kiem soát viec dat phòng/ bàn, nam bat chi tiet thông tin tung phòng/bàn trong quán dang su dung hay còn trong, so luong khách moi phòng/ bàn là bao nhiêu, danh sách món an dã goi tai tung phòng/ bàn và tình trang che bien, phuc vu cua các phòng/bàn.
? CHUYEN PHÒNG/BÀN, GHÉP HÓA DON:

Khi khách hàng di theo nhóm dông và muon ghép bàn, hoac muon chuyen sang bàn khác, ban có the thao tác chuyen phòng/ bàn nhanh chóng neu khách yêu cau. Dong thoi khi thanh toán, ung dung cung cho phép in gop hóa hon tung bàn dã ghép tùy theo lua chon cua khách hàng.
? GOI MÓN TIEN LOI NGAY TRÊN DIEN THOAI/MÁY TÍNH BANG:

Khi khách hàng chon thuc don, thay vì ghi chép và dua xuong bep, nhân viên phuc vu có the chon món cho khách ngay trên máy tính bang/dien thoai. Các thông tin goi món cua khách hàng se duoc gui tu dong xuong bep de che bien.
Khách hàng cung có the de dàng chon thêm các loai topping cho do an, do uong hoac các dich vu dac biet cua cua hàng ban nhu: trà sua thêm trân châu, bánh ngot kem tuoi và giam do ngot ...
? IN HÓA DON  & QUAN LÝ THÔNG TIN TAI BEP:
Khi khách hàng chon xong món, thông tin món an se tu dong duoc chuyen xuong và in tai bep de dau bep bat tay vào che bien.
KiotViet se thông báo chi tiet món nào dang che bien, món nào dã che bien xong cua tung phòng/ bàn de nhân viên phuc vu biet duoc, dua lên cho khách nhanh chóng và chính xác nhat.
Ngoài ra, voi các nhà hàng có su dung máy in bep, ung dung cung se thông báo cho nhân viên boi bàn biet duoc don hàng nào có loi khi in che bien tai máy in cua bep.
? TÍNH NANG QUAN LÝ KARAOKE:

Doi voi các dich vu tính tien theo gio nhu Karaoke, quán Bi-a, ung dung se giúp chu quán theo dõi thoi gian bat dau su dung dich vu và thoi gian ket thúc, kiem tra do an/ do uong khách dã su dung bang dien thoai/ máy tính bang ngay tai phòng và chuyen thông tin hóa don xuong quay thanh toán.
KiotViet - Phan mem quan lý Bar, Café, Nhà Hàng voi giao dien thân thien, don gian, chi mat 10 – 15 phút làm quen là ban dã có the su dung thành thao."

671194210;"Beamz";"ENHANCING LEARNING, THERAPY, & FUN WITH INCLUSIVE INTERACTIVE MUSIC AND LESSONS!

Make great sounding music within minutes, regardless of musical background, and become immersed in this unique music-making and learning experience. This FREE BEAMZ APP includes 24 fun, interactive songs and lessons that promote creativity, free expression, education, early learning, and special needs benefits. All ages, skill levels, and abilities can have fun composing & performing extraordinary interactive music while also receiving a wide variety of learning and therapeutic benefits.

Research has consistently shown that when actively engaging in music, humans use both sides of our brain. 427424412";"AirMic - WiFi Microphone";"Do you need to amplify your voice when presenting in front of big crowd? Have you connected your personal computer to a big screen TV and would like to turn the whole system into a karaoke machine? If so, AirMic can help!

AirMic is an application that transmits audio received from the mic on your iDevice to your personal computer’s front speakers. By using the WiFi network, the audio can be transmitted up to a hundred feet away (depending on network coverage) without decreasing sound quality.
Features:
1. Wirelessly transmits the audio received from an iDevice mic to a remote computer.
2. Controls the remote computer’s system volume.
3. Automatically searches for and connects to the remote computer.
4. Each remote computer can connect up to 4 iDevices.
Application requirements:
1. iPhone/iPod Touch with iOS version 4.0  and above.
2. Any PC or laptop running WinXP,Vista, Windows 7 or Mac OSX 10.5 Intel and above.
4. Your iPhone/iPod Touch and the remote computer must be on the same subnet.
5. The AudioReceiver application must be downloaded and installed on your PC or Mac.

Note: the AudioReceiver application needs to be installed and running on your remote computer before starting up the AirMic. Please download and install the AudioReceiver from the download page of our website www.mbpowertools.net."

323796203;"Play On Cue";"Play On Cue is a music player which cues and plays individual sounds and songs when the Play button is tapped.  When each song has finished, the next song is displayed and ready to play.  Play On Cue intentionally stops automatically after each song.

Play On Cue is intended for theater groups, talent shows, concerts, karaoke, musicians, DJ's, sound engineers - anyone who needs to start each song on a specific cue.  Users can add additional songs, playlists or empty the cue without interrupting playback of the current song. Song title and artist are displayed in large easy to read text along with album artwork (when available).

Use iTunes to create your playlists. Select the playlists in Play On Cue and tap ""Load all songs"" for each set or scene. Sounds or songs will be in the order saved in the playlist.  Songs can be added, removed or reordered while playing.
Play On Cue is a simple way to start sounds or songs ONE SONG AT A TIME when needed in a live performance.
** Play On Cue intentionally stops automatically after each song. **
Support for AirTurn and other BlueTooth remotes can be enabled /disabled in system settings along with support for rotating the display upside down so that the audio cable is out of the way.
Support for AirTurn is DISABLED by default - you MUST ENABLE it in system settings if you want to use it.  Some remote devices should select a different mode to properly control the transport.

When the iPod music player is playing (intermission or before a show), Play On Cue continues to play and monitor the iPod's playlist.  When you are ready to start your show, tap the NEXT or PREVIOUS button to stop the iPod's playback and queue your song list.

Although Play On Cue will stream songs in the cloud from iTunes Match, for best performance, and to prevent a glitch during a performance due to unforeseen network issues, we recommend only playing songs stored locally on your device."

296803692;"Echochops";"The extreme delay machine that you've never heard before.

In short:  This is a Karaoke echo machine.  Words spoken in the iPhone's microphone will come back a few seconds later.  It's like the echo effect you can hear at a mountain.  You can get various kinds of effects by changing the delay time and the feedback rate.

To make music:  Tap on the table - it sounds like ""tock""......""tock"".....""tock""..... Clap your hands - you'll hear ""tock"", ""clap"", ""tock"", ""clap"", ""tock"", ""clap""... You can produce simple musical patterns this way.

Daily life use:  Leave it as it is.  It's fun to hear repeating sounds of ordinary life.  You can use the stereo headset with the mic.  Take a walk with the iPhone in your pocket and enjoy the repeating sounds around you.

In detail: ""Echochops"" produces a feedback delay effect (an echo effect) on the sounds from the iPhone's microphone. The feedback delay is widely used to produce rich vocal and guitar sounds.  It is also used as a special kind of musical performance. You can use ""Echochops"" not only as a ""musical"" application  but also as a ""noisy"" experiment.
Features:
- Input and output level meter
- Input and output level setting
- Delay time setting, within 60 seconds.
- Feedback rate setting, from 0% to 100%
- Direct and Delay balance setting
- Four types of audio filters (Lowpass, Highpass, Bandpass, Notch)
- Audio filter frequency setting
- Audio filer Q setting
- Parameter control by audio input/output levels
- Parameter control by tilting
- Parameter control by rotating (a compass-equipped device only)
- Mode setting to change delay time, ""Glitch"" or ""Funny"".
- Output route setting, headphone/receiver or speaker.
- Tilt angle setting for controlling
- Upside-down portrait mode for efficient use of microphone and speaker
- Delayed sound can be erased
- Works with iPod audio simultaneously
- Background audio playback (iOS 4.0 and later)

[[ ATTENTIONS ]] Due to a latency of an audio input and output, the actual delaying time will be slightly longer than the setting.  A natural feedback through the air may happen because the microphone and speaker are placed closely on the iPhone.  Distorted sounds or harsh grating noises will be produced depending of the setting of parameters.  It would be better NOT to use this application if you cannot stand noisy sounds.
[[ Address of Gratitude ]] Thanks to Mr. Kaoru Sato (EP-4)"

1041950855;"lezen maar! haan hik";"Haan hik is een eenvoudig maar heerlijk verhaaltje voor beginnende lezers. In deze vrolijke app nemen we jouw beginnende lezer stapsgewijs mee op leesavontuur met behulp van de karaoke voorleesfuncties en diversie oefeningen.

Haan hik is één van de zes apps in de reeks Lezen maar!. Naast de apps zijn de verhalen ook beschikbaar als leesboekje. Auteur van de reeks is Heidi Walleghem. Van dezelfde auteur verscheen bij uitgeverij die Keure ook de aanvankelijke leesmethode mol en beer.
Extra info voor ouders en leerkrachten:
- Dit boekje is geschikt voor kinderen die leren lezen.

1039760545;"lezen maar! soep met een bal";"Soep met een bal is een eenvoudig maar heerlijk verhaaltje voor beginnende lezers. In deze vrolijke app nemen we jouw beginnende lezer stapsgewijs mee op leesavontuur met behulp van de karaoke voorleesfuncties en diverse oefeningen.
- Lees voor: terwijl het verhaaltje wordt voorgelezen, licht elk woord op.

- Lees mee: stel het aantal seconden in die de beginnende lezer nodig heeft om een woord zelf te lezen. Na het verstrijken van deze tijd wordt het woord voorgelezen. Zo krijgt het kind auditieve steun bij het lezen.
- Lees zelf: het kind leest op eigen tempo. Zit er toch een moeilijk woord bij? Tik om te horen hoe het woord klinkt.
- Oefen: de lezer oefent alle woorden die in het verhaal voorkomen via de reeksen “ik lees” en “ik schrijf”.

Soep met een bal is één van de zes apps in de reeks Lezen maar!. Naast de apps zijn de verhalen ook beschikbaar als leesboekje. Auteur van de reeks is Heidi Walleghem. Van dezelfde auteur verscheen bij uitgeverij die Keure ook de aanvankelijke leesmethode mol en beer.

- Dit boekje is geschikt voor kinderen die leren lezen.

Who Stole the Moon?"" is an interactive musical picture book application. The fairy tale ""Who Stole the Moon?"" was written by British writer Helen Stratton-Would and illustrated by internationally-acclaimed Russian artist Vlad Gerasimov. It's a story about little Bertie, who dreamed about becoming an astronaut. He loved to watch the moon shining through his skylight window every night as he lay in bed. One evening, though, the moon didn't appear in the sky.

Who Stole the Moon?"" With this serious question, ""detective"" Bertie set out on his adventure. Help solve the mystery! Meet some amazing animal friends. Play games with them and sing together. Join Bertie on his quest with this charming bedtime story that will gently nurture your child's imagination and send him off into the magical world of dreams.
Full version includes:
~ Complete story with fully interactive vivid illustrations.
~ 4 educational games.
~ 8 original songs, plus karaoke.
The songs performed by award-winning American children's singer Susie Tallman and Australian musician Richard Pleasance.
The story is narrated by professional actors in 17 languages.
*** Smart Apps for Kids:

On top of a great story, this app comes loaded with 4 story related games including 9 levels of a matching/memory type game; 16 pictures from the story little hands can paint (with no mess!); a ""tap the lightning bugs to light them up"" game; and 32 puzzles that are either 5x5 or 8x8 in difficulty. Music from the app is also available under ""songs"", in which you can simply be lulled by the light melodies, or hear words added and sung to you.""
*** Tap Scape:
Who Stole The Moon? is a great iPad investment for parents with young children. Perfect for bedtime or for a rainy day activity, this iPad app is worth checking out, so grab it ASAP!"""

458823741;"Old MacDonald for iPad";"Join Old MacDonald on the farm and develop your child’s listening and language skills!
•••  Featured in New & Noteworthy by Apple! •••

Created by Listening and Spoken Language Specialists in conjunction with Early Childhood Teachers, Old MacDonald is a highly interactive learning experience. The app is full of wonderful educational ideas, interactive games, and engaging sounds to encourage the development of listening and language skills in young children. Families of children who have reduced hearing or language difficulties will find the app particularly useful.

Old MacDonald has been designed as a cooperative app for parents and children so they can participate in a variety of shared activities together. Children and parents will be delighted with the beautiful animations, playful dialogue, and fun animal noises. These activities are divided into three sections:
1. Ideas

This section provides strategies and techniques, including instructional videos on how to use Old MacDonald to develop listening and language skills. This is achieved through interactive play, craft, and ideas on how to sing the song differently. These ideas are grouped together depending on your child’s language level:
• Emerging language
• Putting words together
• Putting sentences together
2. Interactive games

There are a variety of fun, fully animated games that target different levels of listening and language skills. With help from mum or dad, your child can choose to play a game that either consolidates or extends their current listening and language abilities. The games are:
• Farmyard animals
Introduces different farm animals and the sounds they make. Poke the animals to see them animate and hear what sounds they make.
• Guess who
Reinforces the animal sounds by having your child identify the animal that made the sound. Introduces the names of the animals and the sound words (e.g. quack quack) they make.
• Record your own sounds
Record you and your child making farm animal noises! Then listen and watch your recordings come to life!
• Help Old MacDonald

Help Old MacDonald find the animal he needs, e.g. “Old MacDonald needs the animal that gives him eggs.” Watch the animals spring to life when you select the right answer. The game extends your child’s vocabulary and understanding of concepts relating to farm animals by learning the role of the animals on the farm.
PLEASE NOTE: Games are not compatible with VoiceOver screen reader.
3. Music and karaoke
Learn the lyrics to Old MacDonald, alternative versions, and related songs. A karaoke style sing-a-long with music and lyrics is a great way to involve your child in singing.
More apps
Old MacDonald is part of our series on ‘Songs for Listening and Language.’

Facebook: Join us on Facebook to keep up to date with upcoming apps –  www.facebook.com/nextsenseau
This app does not contain any third-party analytics
This app does not contain any third-party advertising
There is no user or device data that is share with third parties
This app does not collect any user or device data

417617905;"tapeRecorder HD";"""tapeRecorder HD"" trasforma il tuo dispositivo in un registratore / player musicale a nastro OLD STYLE.
Utile per:
- registrare interviste, lezioni all'università, appunti audio, live music performances
- riprodurre musica / registrazioni contenute nella propria libreria musicale iTunes
Il software permette:
- di effettuare infinite registrazioni con durata infinita (di tipo professionale - utilizzando il microfono del dispositivo)
- memorizza infinite registrazioni nell'archivio (""Archive"") (fino ad esaurimento della memoria fisica del dispositivo)
- assegna automaticamente data ed ora attuali come titolo alla registrazione effettuata (registrazione automatica archivio storico)
- in ogni istante è possibile caricare ed ascoltare le registrazioni effettuate
- utilizzando la tecnologia ""iTunes File Sharing"" tutte le registrazioni possono essere trasferite dal dispositivo al MAC o PC (RECORDING BACKUP)
- utilizzando la tecnologia ""iTunes File Sharing"" tutte le registrazioni possono essere trasferite dal MAC / PC al dispositivo
- permette il caricamento di ogni brano contenuti nella libreria musicale del dispositivo per un successivo ascolto (funzione PLAYER per libreria musicale iTunes)
- ascolto e registrazione parallela:
1) importare una musica dalla libreria di iTunes
2) premere REC
3) premere PLAY
4) cantare sulla musica in riproduzione
RISULTATO: la musica + la voce verranno registrate su un nuovo file audio (funzione REGISTRAZIONE KARAOKE) e memorizzato nell'archivio (""Archive"")
(questi step possono essere ripetuti più volte per creare ad esempio dei cori o una doppia voce)
- REW ed FF nastro lento e veloce (premendo sui tasti REW ed FF il nastro verrà riavviato o portato avanti come avviene nei vecchi registratori a cassette)

1249824094;"Vietnam Travel Guide inVietnam";"Why inVietnam

There are various aspects of each urban center, each land. It is the appearance of a city or a land and the path through history that create the portrait of that city, land. In contemplating an object or going sightseeing in a place, people usually take interest in what is exposed before their eyes, but to understand, to love, or to live with it, people often trace back to the past, the history.

A city or a land itself is not an exception. The fate of a city or a land depends on its attitude towards its own past and history. If a city or a land knows how to love the past and to respect history, its current position will be more steady and the road to the future will be brighter.

The past and the history of a land or a city include various tangible and in tangible things. Relics and landscapes are an important part of the past, the history. Through relics and landscapes, we can see the attitude of our ancestors in dealing with the universe and with their people; we can see the image of many successive generations of those who had lived in that land; we can see the happiness and sadness, contentment and misery, worry and aspiration, sweat and blood of our ancestors on the long road through history and the past of the land.

People in the era of globalization are eagerly in search of both universal and humanity values. The farther and wider we travel, the more we need to turn round to observe our original face. Actually, the differentiation and uniqueness can not be detached from the past, or more precisely, a large part of it is determined by the past and its distinctive history.

Most of us have the need to understand history, or understand the past. And, obviously, the introduction of relics and landscapes is an essential task for each of us. In this way of thinking, we would like to introduce to our readers this mobile application: inViet Nam

inVietnam - Viet Nam Travel Guide contains comprehensive and up to date city guides for 63 destinations like Da Nang, Ha Noi, Sai Gon, Nha Trang, Hoi An, Hue and many other travel destinations in Vietnam. It could work offline, you don't need an internet connection.

781483331;"Musk MIDI Player";"Musk MIDI Player: Your instant MIDI player - just add sounds and MIDI files!
* Load any MIDI file and sound library (a small General MIDI sound font is included)
* You can search the web for MIDI files and download.
* Play MIDI files up to 8 times slower or faster
* Transpose MIDI files.
* Follow the MIDI notes on the keyboard and distinguish different MIDI channels
* Read along the lyrics
* Let the app speak the lyrics during playback
* Let the app announce the bar and beat numbers. So you can easier follow the notes in a printed score.
* Mute or solo tracks or use them to navigate
* Use automatic sound switching or customize the sound associated with each MIDI channel.
* Mix with the original sound. (Deactivated on iOS14, reactivated on iOS15)
Integrated web search:
* Use the built-in web browser to search for MIDI files on the web.
* The browser highlights MIDI (.mid, .midi) and Karaoke (.kar) links.
* Downloaded files play back immediately.
Navigation:
* Jump to a specific position using a slider
* To jump back to that position using the repeat button
* Jump to the position of certain meta-events (lyrics, markers, time signature, key signature and tempo changes)
Supported file formats and extensions:
* MIDI (mid, midi)
* MIDI karaoke (kar)
* Sound fonts (sf2)
* Downloadable Sounds (dls)
* Logic Pro EXS-24 instrument files (exs)
* Audio Unit Presets (aupreset)
* Zip files (zip)
Importing files via:
* ITunes: transmission via Mac or PC
* ICloud: synchronizes the data on all your Apple devices. (Network connection required)
* Other Apps from the manufacturer this app: All of his apps access to the same iCloud directory. (No network connection required)
* Safari: search for a website that offers SoundFonts. Click on the file. Wait until it is downloaded. Then select this app in the ""Open In"" dialog.
* Mail: Select the attachment and select this app in the ""Open In"" dialog.
* Other apps: use the ""Open In"" dialog. (Dropbox, Google Drive, SkyDrive)
Inter-App-Audio, Audiobus and Core-MIDI support:
You can use the audio output of this app in other apps:
* Record the mixed-down audio output in Garageband, AudioShare or other apps.
* Add sound effects in GarageBand, VoiceSynth or other apps.
* Use this App as a MIDI-Generator in Audiobus or in apps that can receive Core-MIDI notes.
Limitations:
* Speech output can not be sent to other apps.
* Which app combinations are possible depends on Your hardware and Your sound fonts.
* Playing MIDI files with many notes per second can push older devices to their limits. When you hear a scraping noise, try lowering the playback rate.
Have fun!"

1214721881;"Earworms: Language Learning";"Do you know what “earworm effect” is? Experience it while you learn languages with catchy music and lyrics that you just can't get out of your head. This highly effective award-winning learning technique uses music as the medium to transport words and phrases of a foreign language into your long-term memory. Start yourlanguage learning now!

Learn Spanish, French, English, German, Italian and other different languages and improve your vocabulary and grammar using the power of music. Earworms plant the words of a foreign language into your head with easy language courses.
Try our language learning with music lyrics demo for free.
THE EARWOMS METHOD
1. Brain-based:

The Earworms method not only provides the words, phrases and grammar that you need for language learning, it also actively anchors them into the auditory cortex of your brain! It’s much more than language courses, it's language learning! Learn French, Spanish, English, Italian, German or Dutch listening to music lyrics.
2. Music is the key:

Using music as the medium to learn languages is not only fun, it is also effective. Firstly, music puts the learner into the optimum state of consciousness for learning different languages. Secondly, music lyrics learning allows repetition (a prerequisite for language learning). On top of that, music engages and stimulates both hemispheres of the brain, unleashing more learning potential.
3. Chunking:

Instead of language learning in terms of individual words and grammar, the Earworms approach immerses the learner in real-life dialogues and expressions with lyrics. These are broken down into bite-size chunks, practiced rhythmically with music and then reconstructed into full sentences. This gives the learner a strong sense of how real language courses are constructed and learning French, Spanish, German, Italian, English and other different languages and their vocabulary becomes easy.
IMPORTANT FEATURES
* Developed by language teaching experts.
* Convenient. 6-9 minute tracks. Listen and learn track by track, any time, anywhere.
* Audio-visual experience with 'karaoke-like' live lyrics feature.
* Specific unambiguous goals. 200+ optimally selected sets of words and phrases for language learning.
* Measurable. Easy tracking of progress of your language courses.
* Target language spoken by native speakers - so correct pronunciation is acquired automatically.
* Relevant. Carefully chosen content-rich language. Based on the CEF (Common European Framework) and immediately useful to the learner.

* Time-bound. The musical memory method enables real rapid progress. E.g. you can learn to count up to 999 in Mandarin in an hour (!) or retain and recall words, phrases and structures in one language level within a couple of weeks.
* Educational discounts are available. Visit www.earwormslearning.com/support/teachers
LANGUAGES CURRENTLY AVAILABLE

French + German + Italian + Spanish (European) + Spanish (Lat. American) + Mandarin + Cantonese + Japanese + Arabic + Portuguese (European) + Portuguese (Brazilian) + Russian + Greek + Turkish + Polish + English + Dutch
LEVELS
There are 3 learning levels available, which will take you up to intermediate level (CEF level A2).

* Volume 1. Within a few hours of listening to this volume, you'll have enough vocabulary knowledge of a language to be able to deal with real-life situations like taking a taxi, at the hotel, at the restaurant, requesting, polite phrases, finding your way, numbers, dealing with problems and so on.
* Volume 2. This language course will soon have you talking about yourself, chatting and even flirting!
* Volume 3. Here you learn more useful everyday situations while going more into the structure, the grammatical rules of the language while improving your vocabulary.
NOTE: the app includes a demo of full tracks of all learn languages available – and is free to download. You can then purchase the full courses from within the app."

1106224733;"Muzoma";"Muzoma is a musical productivity app that can literally give you your band in your hand.

If you are an artist, composer, performer, band member, sound engineer, producer, DJ, karaoke author, busker, publisher, or music content creator, some or all of the features of Muzoma will be of interest to you.

Muzoma allows the playback and recording, organisation and sharing of multi-channel / multi-track and / or stereo / mono backing tracks synchronized with lyric and chord cues on the device and optionally via Apple Airplay (tm) and / or Muzoma's band share peer to peer feature.
Test out the multi-channel playback** on your own hardware using the demo song at http://www.muzoma.co.uk
View the Muzoma User Guide available to download in the iBooks store to see the features available in Muzoma Producer.
With the in-app purchase of the Producer version, you can create, develop and share your own productions with other Muzoma users.

Muzoma Producer is designed to be the next step on from your Digital Audio Workstation (DAW).  It's the is app you will want to use after your Logic, ProTools, Cubase, Reason or Ableton* recording session.

You can take the output from your DAW as 'stems' in MP3 format, import these into Muzoma, include the mix-down as the guide track, include an audio click track, and add the lyrics and chord cues to the production.  Muzoma Producer works with iCloud (and other cloud services) enabling content to be easily imported and included in a Muzoma song.  Once created, the song is then ready to share or add to a set for sharing and conveniently on the iPad or iPhone to use live and in a multi-channel, multi-track situation(**).  From version 2.0 Muzoma supports the AudioShare app for both single audio file import/export and multiple file using the .zip file bundles.
From version 2.0 Muzoma allows importing of existing content from Karaoke-Version.com, including support for importing multi-track Custom Backing Tracks.

From version 2.2 Muzoma now supports exporting a set for playback natively from a Cymatic LP16 and imports into Cymatic's uTool2 allowing playback to the LP16 or internal sound from a Mac or PC from uToool2.

Muzoma is unique because it offers multi-channel audio output (including multiple MP3) to popular iOS compatible audio hardware(*) such as the Midas M32 / Behringer X32, Cymatic Audio LP16 and uTrack24, Antelope Orion 32, Focusrite Scarlett and iTrack and other class compliant audio interfaces all via the Apple USB camera connection kit which makes it great for playback of in-ear click tracks, missing band member scenarios, virtual sound checks or just expanding the band with sound effects, exotic instruments, doubled tracks and keyboard sounds.

Muzoma Producer includes a song editor for writing lyrics and chord editing.  Once the lyrics and chords are created and associated with a guide track, it's then simply a case of using the timing editor to associate the chord and lyric events with the song.
Other Producer features include:
A multi-channel / multi-track mixer with recording facility and file import / export features and midi automation
Midi control features allowing remote control of Muzoma, Muzoma can also send midi commands
Import / Export the popular chord pro format as well as text file
Copyright, author and ownership markers
PDF / HTML / Text format export
Air Printing
Practice your individual part on your own with band backing by recording the band live and then muting your own track.
(*) Companies and brands mentioned are examples of compatibility, the companies mentioned are not directly associated with Muzoma Ltd

(**)  Note that a more recent iDevice might be required to achieve the highest number of channels in a multi-channel output situation - we have tested up to 32 mono on an iPhone SE 64gig.  Use the free player version and download the multi-channel test sets at Muzoma.co.uk to verify your hardware before purchasing the in app producer version."
